title: Tiger 10.4.11 for iMac 7.1 and nevest (iBrain Pack)
description:
Retail Multilanguage Tiger 10.4.11 + AppleTV Pack + All update to November 2008.
Tiger for not supported iMac.

If you want Tiger on nevest iMac that what you need.

This file is a DMG (Disk Image) made with the Disk Utility.  It contains the Tiger OS.  Also, this release actually boots the clean Tiger 10.4.11 on iMac 7.1.

How-To:  Simply plug in and turn on the drive you want to install the DMG to, open Disk Utility, Select the drive to restore to, click Restore, and select the Tiger.dmg file.

This file, when installed, is around 8.05GB.

This Build contein pathed Front Row to AppleTV version.

Russian is default languege, for change it, just go to sys pref ;)
